Some configuration files should be created, including:

site.php
	with the following information:
	
	<?php
	$il_site_name = '<sitename>';
	$il_style = '<style>';
	
	$il_data_server	= '<database-server>';	// default is localhost
	$il_data_database	= '<database-name>';	// default is interlecto
	$il_data_prefix	= '<database-prefix>';	// default is interlecto
	$il_data_user	= '<database-user>';	// default is root
	$il_data_password	= '<database-user-password>';	// default is blank
	?>
	
	Note that this file might be created by the install utility.

